      "rationale": "Stiffness: FEA 187 N/mm vs experimental 191 ± 8 N/mm (2.1% diff, E/uval = 0.49). Yield force: FEA 312 N vs experimental 318 ± 14 N (1.9% diff, E/uval = 0.43). Force at 40 mm: FEA 428 N vs experimental 435 ± 19 N (1.6% diff, E/uval = 0.37). All within acceptance bounds."
    },
